verses.text: And in the seventh month , on the first \add day\add* of the month , ye shall have an holy convocation ; ye shall do no servile work : it is a day of blowing the trumpets unto you.
And ye shall offer a burnt offering for a sweet savour unto the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd*; one young bullock , one ram , \add and\add* seven lambs of the first year without blemish :
And their meat offering \add shall be of\add* flour mingled with oil , three tenth deals for a bullock , \add and\add* two tenth deals for a ram ,
And one tenth deal for one lamb , throughout the seven lambs :
And one kid of the goats \add for\add* a sin offering , to make an atonement for you:

Beside the burnt offering of the month , and his meat offering , and the daily burnt offering , and his meat offering , and their drink offerings , according unto their manner , for a sweet savour , a sacrifice made by fire unto the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd*. \p
¶ And ye shall have on the tenth \add day\add* of this seventh month an holy convocation ; and ye shall afflict your souls : ye shall not do any work \add therein:\add*

But ye shall offer a burnt offering unto the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* \add for\add* a sweet savour ; one young bullock , one ram , \add and\add* seven lambs of the first year ; they shall be unto you without blemish :
And their meat offering \add shall be of\add* flour mingled with oil , three tenth deals to a bullock , \add and\add* two tenth deals to one ram ,
A several tenth deal for one lamb , throughout the seven lambs :
One kid of the goats \add for\add* a sin offering ; beside the sin offering of atonement , and the continual burnt offering , and the meat offering of it, and their drink offerings. \p
¶ And on the fifteenth day of the seventh month ye shall have an holy convocation ; ye shall do no servile work , and ye shall keep a feast unto the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* seven days :

And ye shall offer a burnt offering , a sacrifice made by fire , of a sweet savour unto the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd*; thirteen young bullocks , two rams , \add and\add* fourteen lambs of the first year ; they shall be without blemish :
And their meat offering \add shall be of\add* flour mingled with oil , three tenth deals unto every bullock of the thirteen bullocks , two tenth deals to each ram of the two rams ,
And a several tenth deal to each lamb of the fourteen lambs :
And one kid of the goats \add for\add* a sin offering ; beside the continual burnt offering , his meat offering , and his drink offering. \p
¶ And on the second day \add ye shall offer\add* twelve young bullocks , two rams , fourteen lambs of the first year without spot :
And their meat offering and their drink offerings for the bullocks , for the rams , and for the lambs , \add shall be\add* according to their number , after the manner :
And one kid of the goats \add for\add* a sin offering ; beside the continual burnt offering , and the meat offering thereof, and their drink offerings. \p
¶ And on the third day eleven bullocks , two rams , fourteen lambs of the first year without blemish ;
And their meat offering and their drink offerings for the bullocks , for the rams , and for the lambs , \add shall be\add* according to their number , after the manner :
And one goat \add for\add* a sin offering ; beside the continual burnt offering , and his meat offering , and his drink offering. \p
¶ And on the fourth day ten bullocks , two rams , \add and\add* fourteen lambs of the first year without blemish :
Their meat offering and their drink offerings for the bullocks , for the rams , and for the lambs , \add shall be\add* according to their number , after the manner :
And one kid of the goats \add for\add* a sin offering ; beside the continual burnt offering , his meat offering , and his drink offering. \p
¶ And on the fifth day nine bullocks , two rams , \add and\add* fourteen lambs of the first year without spot :
And their meat offering and their drink offerings for the bullocks , for the rams , and for the lambs , \add shall be\add* according to their number , after the manner :
And one goat \add for\add* a sin offering ; beside the continual burnt offering , and his meat offering , and his drink offering. \p
¶ And on the sixth day eight bullocks , two rams , \add and\add* fourteen lambs of the first year without blemish :
And their meat offering and their drink offerings for the bullocks , for the rams , and for the lambs , \add shall be\add* according to their number , after the manner :
And one goat \add for\add* a sin offering ; beside the continual burnt offering , his meat offering , and his drink offering. \p
¶ And on the seventh day seven bullocks , two rams , \add and\add* fourteen lambs of the first year without blemish :
And their meat offering and their drink offerings for the bullocks , for the rams , and for the lambs , \add shall be\add* according to their number , after the manner :
And one goat \add for\add* a sin offering ; beside the continual burnt offering , his meat offering , and his drink offering. \p
¶ On the eighth day ye shall have a solemn assembly : ye shall do no servile work \add therein:\add*

But ye shall offer a burnt offering , a sacrifice made by fire , of a sweet savour unto the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd*: one bullock , one ram , seven lambs of the first year without blemish :
Their meat offering and their drink offerings for the bullock , for the ram , and for the lambs , \add shall be\add* according to their number , after the manner :
And one goat \add for\add* a sin offering ; beside the continual burnt offering , and his meat offering , and his drink offering.

These \add things\add* ye shall do unto the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* in your set feasts , beside your vows , and your freewill offerings , for your burnt offerings , and for your meat offerings , and for your drink offerings , and for your peace offerings.\f + \fr 29.39 \ft do: or, offer\f*
And Moses told the children of Israel according to all that the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* commanded Moses.
